snippet.title: Predators Android Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as the Predator in this officially licensed game based on the latest chapter of the hit franchise PREDATORS™!
Hone your tracking skills and killing techniques to lethal precision as you collect the most prized trophies -- heads of human prey.
